Description:
    Creates a new basic derby 0.6 application.

Options:
    Jade: Include Jade
    Stylus: Include Stylus
    Redis: Include Redis

Example:
    yo derby [--coffee]

    This will create:
        package.json: Development packages installed by npm.

        src/: Your derby 0.6 application files.
        components/: Your local components.
        views/: Your template files.
        styles/: Your css/stylus files.
        test/: Unit tests for your application.
